{"tid":1747534,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"你班mon po 中學雞同我入一入黎","createTime":"2019-11-23T09:14:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-23T16:54:00.000Z","uid":176327,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"80187348740ff9845e6697983818c51f62affdd4","tid":1747534,"uid":176327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:14:45.000Z","msg":"[轉載]<br />\n<br />\n我哋係<strong>Stand by U （和你入U）</strong><br />\n成立目的係為咗幫助被抗爭影響學業嘅應屆DSE考生<br />\n到今屆DSE完結前一眾tutor都會以義教形式進行<br />\n教學形式會以影片為主 令更多學生受惠<br />\n除影片外，某科目我地仲會提供notes 筆記 mockpaper pastpaper等等<br />\n有任何問題可到youtube channel嘅comment section留言<br />\n<br />\n中六學生請去填咗以下呢張form等我地嘅tutor因材施教<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScSp4IrLNNxR6neGsf22VSxUyMNUkdcSDhE24UFjE4Ua3sStg/viewform?usp=pp_url\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScSp4IrLNNxR6neGsf22VSxUyMNUkdcSDhE24UFjE4Ua3sStg%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dpp_url&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=063dd171\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScSp4IrLNNxR6neGsf22VSxUyMNUkdcSDhE24UFjE4Ua3sStg/viewform?usp=pp_url</a><br />\n<br />\n想加入成為導師/developer 或留意最新動向 (youtube channel名，ig page)<br />\n請即follow <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/yelloweconomist/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fyelloweconomist%2F&d=SNVPshlwtiHAgFu1pF0TpKjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=5991d929\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/yelloweconomist/</a>"},{"pid":"31ce46a0f2ef6c975d6d52ea7619af9a039dd01e","tid":1747534,"uid":135824,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T09:17:58.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咪撚做毅進仔呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{